profile: We use a safe alternative to heavy equipment. We use Hydro excavating, this uses water and vacuum pressure to remove soil/rocks. We can work directly over gas/water/bell or hydro lines that are buried. We are governed by the TSSA and E@USA and OHSA. We also do camera inspections with full digital reporting on sewer/storm or household sanitary lines.
